{"tid":1627040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲all in港島？ 打游擊呀","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:32:47.000Z","uid":310373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b7219baabee4459efd337c710668faf7f757b8","tid":1627040,"uid":310373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<br />\n今時今日仲見到有人吹雞港島<br />\n主張和理非三百萬遊行咁話<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講真望住928 929都知冇可能啦<br />\n唔係話冇咁多香港人想出<br />\n而係依家嘅港府唔會再容許你咁做</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仗係要打  但唔係咁打<br />\n上兵伐謀  善之善者不戰而屈人之兵<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地冇人冇資源策略都冇埋打條毛？<br />\n咩叫打游擊？<br />\n<br />\n敵進我退  敵駐我擾<br />\n敵疲我打  敵退我追</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">阿爺當年都係靠打游擊先有今日</span><br />\n依家用到緊急法落老解so what?<br />\n咪由佢玩囉有咩所謂？<br />\n<br />\n依家黨鐵商場閂哂<br />\n擺明你一出就隊冧你<br />\n請問硬碰硬對我地有咩好處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反試諗下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">如果全世界合作一齊玩失蹤</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢咪一定會開翻解禁<br />\n佢開翻我地咪再出<br />\n再封再匿再開再出<br />\n<br />\n退一萬步講，就算真係好想出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔應該再all in港島<br />\n呢個月出過港島打仗嘅都知有幾難走</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真心要玩咪快閃打地區打陣地戰囉<br />\n呢度搞下，個度搞下<br />\nPopo黎咪閃，走咪翻轉頭玩過</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">拿 克警就得三萬<br />\n玩都玩死佢啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不如大家想像下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">班popo跑勻十八區又拉唔到人踢垃圾桶個畫面？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都幾治癒呀<br />\n<br />\n拿 要講嘅就講哂喇<br />\n戴翻個頭盔先<br />\n以上純粹個人意見<br />\n但無論出唔出<br />\n出邊度又或做乜嘢都係各位嘅選擇<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點都好唔該唔好死<br />\n&nbsp;聽日唔係 End game<br />\n我地要留住條命煲底除罩相見唱榮光！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d8df51c5350f77e29c85c93755f0ae7ef46a433d","tid":1627040,"uid":310373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd51a25bf1b370bb13badaef4e5caba827b0ca80","tid":1627040,"uid":310373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:12:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d14d9fe5073bd226dc7df1be0ccaba08921a058","tid":1627040,"uid":310373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc71008b8f0d33d1eb37d269bc03c7214a1d47d5","tid":1627040,"uid":310373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}